, \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The flame has been extinguished and the Olympic flag lowered, folded and passed on to 2028 host city Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1405, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 6.968234883912596e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The flame\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1344}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And after Australia's most successful games ever, the conversation now shifts to how to replicate that winning formula.\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.7928776379011111, \"rank\": 0.25898525845216086, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the conversation\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"that winning formula\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1524}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tracy Holmes:You know, what it says, when you look at the medal tally and you look at the nations that finish on top and Australia has finished in fourth, it shows that the countries that invest most money in sport win the most medals.\", \"from\": 1527, \"to\": 1762, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1527, \"end\": 1532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spencer_Tracy\", \"score\": 0.7878936277464985, \"rank\": 0.15050793078323052, \"text\": \"Tracy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spencer_Tracy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spencer_Tracy\"}, {\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"score\": 0.9999999746792131, \"rank\": 2.5320840002110893e-08, \"text\": \"Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sherlock_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 1648, \"end\": 1657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.7928776379011111, \"rank\": 0.25898525845216086, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medal tally\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"the nations\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1624}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1643}, {\"ngram\": \"the countries\", \"from\": 1696, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"most money\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"the most medals\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unfortunately, it's that simple.\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1795, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nick Grimm:Tracey Holmes is a professorial fellow in sport at the University of Canberra and host of the Sports Ambassador podcast.\", \"from\": 1797, \"to\": 1928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tracey_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tracey Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tracey_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tracey_Holmes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a professorial fellow\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1855}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1873}, {\"ngram\": \"Canberra\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"host\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 1894}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sports Ambassador podcast\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1927}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As she points out, right now the nation is cashing in on efforts to revamp the Australian Sports Commission and an athlete-focused investment that it's hoped will keep on delivering for another two games at least.\", \"from\": 1929, \"to\": 2142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2008, \"end\": 2036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Sports Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"efforts\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete-focused investment\", \"from\": 2041, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"another two games\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tracy Holmes:All of this aimed on what people are calling the green and golden runway to Brisbane 2032 and so what we have seen is that with more of an intense focus and a real honing in on exactly what athletes need in order to get the best performance out of themselves in these big moments, it does pay dividends.\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"the green and golden runway\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2229}, {\"ngram\": \"Brisbane\", \"from\": 2233, \"to\": 2241}, {\"ngram\": \"an intense focus\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"a real honing\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2355}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2369}, {\"ngram\": \"the best performance\", \"from\": 2377, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"these big moments\", \"from\": 2419, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"dividends\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Obviously, it costs a lot of money.\", \"from\": 2461, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2481, \"to\": 2486}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 2490, \"to\": 2495}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nick Grimm:But in a cost of living crisis and with billions of dollars of infrastructure still needing to be built, there is going to be plenty of competition for the funding needed to bring home gold when Australia again hosts the Olympics eight years from now.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2498, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"score\": 0.8099742516144074, \"rank\": 0.23460714700964655, \"text\": \"Nick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\"}, {\"begin\": 2503, \"end\": 2508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brothers_Grimm\", \"score\": 0.9998802489720197, \"rank\": 9.21736798850086e-05, \"text\": \"Grimm\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brothers_Grimm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brothers_Grimm\"}, {\"begin\": 2704, \"end\": 2713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.7928776379011111, \"rank\": 0.25898525845216086, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cost\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"living crisis\", \"from\": 2526, \"to\": 2539}, {\"ngram\": \"billions\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"dollars\", \"from\": 2561, \"to\": 2568}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2586}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 2635, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"competition\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2656}, {\"ngram\": \"the funding\", \"from\": 2661, \"to\": 2672}, {\"ngram\": \"home gold\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2738}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adjunct Professor Colin Dwyer is with Queensland's James Cook University.\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2799, \"end\": 2809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.5858927028195948, \"rank\": 0.5582137410952425, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 2812, \"end\": 2833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"James Cook University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Cook_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adjunct Professor Colin Dwyer\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Colin Dwyer:You know, we have only got eight years in Brisbane in order to get all the stadiums built, to get all the railways built, to get all the roads built and to get the athletes village built, to get the media centre built.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 3066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2890, \"end\": 2898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999954493433, \"rank\": 4.3599118498785805e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"eight years\", \"from\": 2875, \"to\": 2886}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2907}, {\"ngram\": \"all the stadiums\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2931}, {\"ngram\": \"all the railways\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 2962}, {\"ngram\": \"all the roads\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2990}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes village\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3028}, {\"ngram\": \"the media centre\", \"from\": 3043, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are hotels and accommodation facilities that need to be built to accommodate not just the athletes but also the spectators and the officials as well.\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hotels\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3083}, {\"ngram\": \"accommodation facilities\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"not just the athletes\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3171}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectators\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3195}, {\"ngram\": \"the officials\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So you can see where all this is going.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We are now looking at, on my table, around about $62 billion worth of direct and indirect and induced expenditure that's required to build or put the Brisbane Olympics on.\", \"from\": 3263, \"to\": 3434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my table\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3297}, {\"ngram\": \"about $62 billion worth\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3329}, {\"ngram\": \"direct and indirect and induced expenditure\", \"from\": 3333, \"to\": 3376}, {\"ngram\": \"the Brisbane Olympics\", \"from\": 3409, \"to\": 3430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now, that's different to what Paris is because Paris had 95% of its stadiums and infrastructure in place and I believe that Los Angeles is in a similar position.\", \"from\": 3435, \"to\": 3596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3465, \"end\": 3470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 4.0453451775241375e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3482, \"end\": 3487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 4.0453451775241375e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3559, \"end\": 3570, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 6.968234883912596e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"95%\", \"from\": 3492, \"to\": 3495}, {\"ngram\": \"its stadiums\", \"from\": 3499, \"to\": 3511}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3530}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3539}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar position\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But we have to build the stadiums in Brisbane and we have to build the indirect transport facilities to accommodate all the people that will be coming.\", \"from\": 3597, \"to\": 3748, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3634, \"end\": 3642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"score\": 0.9999999954493433, \"rank\": 4.3599118498785805e-09, \"text\": \"Brisbane\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brisbane\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the stadiums\", \"from\": 3618, \"to\": 3630}, {\"ngram\": \"the indirect transport facilities\", \"from\": 3664, \"to\": 3697}, {\"ngram\": \"all the people\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3727}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nick Grimm:And that's likely to require an Olympian effort just to get things ready to host the games.\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3750, \"end\": 3754, \"title\": \"http://d