m\": 4292, \"to\": 4300}, {\"ngram\": \"the head\", \"from\": 4304, \"to\": 4312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I mean, not only do we need people, but we need the best people, just like an Olympics team.\", \"from\": 4314, \"to\": 4406, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4342, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"the best people\", \"from\": 4362, \"to\": 4377}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympics team\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, you know, to get these projects done and done well and so that we are leading the world stage.\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4505, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these projects\", \"from\": 4428, \"to\": 4442}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I have concerns with the fact that our economy has been performing well and we have got skill shortages everywhere with projects nationally outside of the Olympics that need to be done.\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4695, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4539}, {\"ngram\": \"our economy\", \"from\": 4545, \"to\": 4556}, {\"ngram\": \"skill shortages\", \"from\": 4598, \"to\": 4613}, {\"ngram\": \"projects\", \"from\": 4630, \"to\": 4638}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So how are we going, you know, there needs to be more thought into the skills, talent, training, development of our skills base so that we can get these projects done.\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more thought\", \"from\": 4745, \"to\": 4757}, {\"ngram\": \"the skills\", \"from\": 4763, \"to\": 4773}, {\"ngram\": \"talent\", \"from\": 4775, \"to\": 4781}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 4783, \"to\": 4791}, {\"ngram\": \"development\", \"from\": 4793, \"to\": 4804}, {\"ngram\": \"our skills base\", \"from\": 4808, \"t